==Infiltration II==
===Talking to Servius===
* {{tcond|If the player does not have all of the requirements to start the quest:}}
** {{tmissing}}
* {{tcond|If the player has all of the requirements to start the quest:}}
** '''Servius, Teokan of Ralos:''' Nilsal, my child. Your arrival is well timed.
** '''Player:''' It is?
** '''Servius, Teokan of Ralos:''' Yes. The Queen would like to speak with you.
** {{tselect|Start The Final Dawn quest?}}
** {{topt|Yes.}}
*** '''Player:''' Now?
*** '''Servius, Teokan of Ralos:''' Indeed. She is waiting for you upstairs. I will go on ahead and let her know you are here.
*** {{qact|A cutscene opens with the player meeting with the council.}}
*** '''Queen Zyanyi Arkan:''' I am told you were with my son when he was captured?
*** '''Player:''' Yes, my Queen.
*** '''Queen Zyanyi Arkan:''' You followed along with this plan of his, knowing that in doing so, you were supporting him in disobeying an order from his Queen?
*** '''Player:''' Yes, my Queen.
*** '''Queen Zyanyi Arkan:''' You do not strike me as a fool, so why do you play the part of one?
*** '''Player:''' I can fix this. I promise you, I will find Itzla and I will rescue him.
*** '''Queen Zyanyi Arkan:''' Why should I trust you? Because my son did? Tell me, which recent event was it that suggested to you that he was of sound judgement?
*** '''Servius, Teokan of Ralos:''' With respect, my Queen, were it not for [player name] here, I would have died at the hands of the Emissaries. I believe [he has/she has/they have] earned our trust.
*** '''Queen Zyanyi Arkan:''' Trust is like a blade. If not maintained, it fails when you need it most.
*** '''Servius, Teokan of Ralos:''' Then let us give our iknami here the opportunity to regain our trust.
*** '''Queen Zyanyi Arkan:''' Hmm...
*** '''Queen Zyanyi Arkan:''' You seem to have made quite the impression, outsider. Both Servius and my son have taken a liking to you.
*** '''Queen Zyanyi Arkan:''' Prove them right. Rectify this situation.
*** '''Player:''' I will. Where should I begin?
*** '''Queen Zyanyi Arkan:''' We need to avoid outright aggression. The safety of my son cannot be risked. I understand you were able to infiltrate the Emissaries and gain access to their temple?
*** '''Player:''' That's right.
*** '''Queen Zyanyi Arkan:''' Then do so again. Gather any information you can on what they are doing with my son, then return to me here. Do not give me a reason to regret this decision.
*** '''Player:''' I won't let you down. You have my word.
*** '''Servius, Teokan of Ralos:''' Good luck, my child. May the sun light your way.
*** {{qact|The cutscene ends, teleporting the player upstairs of the Sunrise Palace.}}
** {{topt|No.}}
*** '''Player:''' I just need to do something else first, but I'll be back soon.
*** '''Servius, Teokan of Ralos:''' Don't take too long. The Queen doesn't like to be kept waiting.
*** {{tact|end}}

====Talking to Servius again before going to meet with Queen Zyanyi====
* '''Servius, Teokan of Ralos:''' The Queen is waiting, my child. Let us go and speak with her.
* {{tact|above}}

====Talking to Servius again after meeting with Queen Zyanyi====
