* '''Player:''' Thank you. We'll have Itzla back soon. I promise.
* '''Servius, Teokan of Ralos:''' You have the dedication of a true servant of Ralos. Keep safe, my child.
* {{tact|end}}

====Talking to Queen Zyanyi again====
* '''Queen Zyanyi Arkan:''' You have a job to do. Return to the Twilight Temple and uncover any information you may have missed when you were last there.
* '''Player:''' I'll go right away.
* '''Queen Zyanyi Arkan:''' Good. Don't let me down.
* {{tact|end}}

===Entering the Twilight Temple===
* {{tcond|If the player is not wearing the emissary robes:}}
** '''Emissary Ascended:''' Hey! You don't have permission to go in there!
** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player is wearing the emissary robes:}}
** {{qact|A cutscene opens with Metzli leading a sermon.}}
** '''Augur Metzli:''' ... and with the guidance of Ralos and Ranul, who stand beside us in our fight, we will be victorious!
** '''Augur Metzli:''' I know recent setbacks have you questioning. I know you have concerns. You need not whisper them in the shadows, for you are free to question. More than that, you are encouraged to question!
** '''Augur Metzli:''' After all, was it not your questions that brought you here? Did you not dare to ask them while others shied away in fear?
** '''Augur Metzli:''' Remember this: We are the doubters! We are the outcasts! Society shunned us for it, but only those who question everything will ever find the truth.
** '''Augur Metzli:''' And that truth? That is what we fight for. That is what will bring about the Final Dawn!
** '''Augur Metzli:''' Let me now assure you, these setbacks have done nothing to stop us! The road to Mokhaiotl is clearer than ever! We have no need for the Teokan any more!
** '''Augur Metzli:''' Bring out the prisoner!
** {{qact|An Emissary Ascended brings out Prince Itzla, stripped of clothing.}}
** '''Augur Metzli:''' See how the rulers of this kingdom are powerless against us. Itzla Arkan, heir to the throne of Varlamore, is now our prisoner!
** '''Prince Itzla Arkan:''' You love it, don't you? Standing on a stage spouting nonsense to a bunch of fanatics! It means nothing, Metzli!
** '''Augur Metzli:''' People like you always fear the truth. Do you know why? Because without your lies, all that you do, all that you live for, is meaningless.
** '''Augur Metzli:''' But your fear, it can now end. Here, you finally have a purpose. Here, you can finally serve Ralos and Ranul.
** '''Augur Metzli:''' Do you not see? The blood of the Teokan runs through your veins. You are now the key to the Final Dawn!
** '''Prince Itzla Arkan:''' You want my blood? Take it! Just make sure you take it all! At least that way I won't have to listen to the garbage you spew any more!
** '''Augur Metzli:''' Listen to the anger in his voice. It is a poor attempt to mask his fear. We need not fear though, for our purpose is clear.
** '''Augur Metzli:''' Go now, for time is short, and there is much left to do. It will soon be time to deliver Twilight's Promise. It will soon be time for the Final Dawn!
** {{qact|The cutscene ends as Itzla is taken away.}}
** '''Player:''' Hmm... They brought Itzla in from downstairs...
** {{tact|end}}

