===Entering the backroom===
* {{qact|A cutscene plays in which the player enters the backroom.}}
* '''Player:''' There must be something useful here...
* {{qact|The player walks into the northern room.}}
* '''Player:''' Let's see...
* {{qact|The sound of a door opening is heard.}}
* '''Player:''' Uh oh...
* '''Furia Tullus:''' ... not to mention what happens when the Queen sends her forces to recover the Prince.
* '''Augur Metzli:''' The Queen will not dare put her son in danger. Your worries are unfounded. Besides, I've already made arrangements for him to be moved elsewhere.
* '''Furia Tullus:''' Unfounded? Do you not see how risky this plan is? We should have stuck with Servius rather than revealing ourselves.
* '''Augur Metzli:''' And if the opportunity presents itself, Servius will still make for a valid option. The trick here isn't to have one plan, it's to have many. We have enough options available that one of them will bear fruit.
* '''Furia Tullus:''' It won't matter how many options we have if we don't live long enough to see them through. You keep gambling with our future here!
* '''Augur Metzli:''' You should have more faith, Furia. Look at your brother. He's a true believer now.
* '''Furia Tullus:''' A fool is what he is.
* '''Augur Metzli:''' Good job we have many uses for fools then...
* {{qact|The cutscene ends.}}
* '''Player:''' That was close...
* {{tact|end}}

