==Home Invasion==
===Talking to Queen Zyanyi or Servius===
* '''Queen Zyanyi Arkan:''' You've returned. I trust that means you have news for us?
* '''Player:''' I do. Itzla was being held at the temple, but they've now moved him elsewhere.
* '''Queen Zyanyi Arkan:''' Where?
* '''Player:''' I don't know, but I did also find out that they have some sort of plan for him. They called him the key to the Final Dawn. Something to do with him having Servius' blood.
* '''Servius, Teokan of Ralos:''' My blood? Do they wish to trigger the Gathering?
* '''Player:''' The Gathering? What's the Gathering?
* '''Queen Zyanyi Arkan:''' What it is isn't important right now. Do not lose focus on the matter at hand. If you don't know where they took my son, then how do you intend to find out?
* '''Player:''' I discovered that Forebearer Janus, a senior member of the Emissaries, is living right here in Fortis in a cult safe house. I was thinking we could capture him and find out what he knows.
* '''Queen Zyanyi Arkan:''' Where is this safe house?
* '''Player:''' Directly opposite a bank apparently.
* '''Servius, Teokan of Ralos:''' Well, there are no houses opposite the eastern bank, so it must be the one looking over the western bank.
* '''Queen Zyanyi Arkan:''' Then let's not waste any time. Adventurer, I will dispatch Captain Vibia of the Knights of Varlamore to this property. You will meet her there. Secure the property with her and capture this Forebearer Janus.
* '''Player:''' I'll head over there at once.
* '''Queen Zyanyi Arkan:''' Good. May the sun light your way.
* {{tact|end}}

====Talking to Servius again====
* '''Servius, Teokan of Ralos:''' Nilsal, my child. The Queen has given you a job to do. I suggest you get going. Keep safe out there.
* {{tact|end}}

