* '''Captain Vibia:''' Dogs. There's one outside and at least one more in the house. I don't expect them to take kindly to intruders.
* '''Player:''' So what's our plan?
* '''Captain Vibia:''' We will secure the house and prepare a trap to capture this cultist leader upon their return. As we don't know exactly when that will be, I suggest we move quickly.
* '''Captain Vibia:''' First up, we need a way inside. I will keep watch out here while you find us that way in.
* '''Player:''' Okay, I'll get to work.
* {{tact|end}}

