===Interrogating Janus===
* {{tbox|pic=Key (Forebearer Janus) detail.png|You search Janus and find a key to the basement.}}
* '''Player:''' I've found the basement key.
* '''Captain Vibia:''' Good. Down there will work nicely for interrogation. You get him ready. I'll fetch the Queen...
* {{qact|A cutscene plays. Queen Zyanyi, her Kualti, and Servius arrive and gather in Janus' basement.}}
* '''Forebearer Janus:''' The Queen herself? Such an honour. Don't think for one second that I'm going to tell you anything though. Even death itself doesn't scare me.
* '''Queen Zyanyi Arkan:''' Really? I've known a lot of people claim death doesn't scare them. From afar, bravery comes easy, but then the moment finally comes when they stare death in the face...
* {{qact|The Queen walks toward Janus.}}
* '''Queen Zyanyi Arkan:''' That's when they break. If you think you're the exception, you will soon be disappointed.
* '''Forebearer Janus:''' Ha! You are out of touch, my Queen. I am a herald of the Final Dawn! For us, death is a glory to be celebrated!
* '''Queen Zyanyi Arkan:''' Then celebrate it you will, but first, you will talk.
* '''Queen Zyanyi Arkan:''' Leave me with him. Alone.
* {{tbox|You leave the Queen with Forebearer Janus...}}
* {{qact|As the group leaves the two of them alone, the screen fades to black while various sounds of an unarmed man being assaulted can be heard. The screen then returns to normal, with the group returning as well. Janus is lying on the ground.}}
* '''Player:''' What happened?
* '''Queen Zyanyi Arkan:''' He talked.
* {{qact|The cutscene ends.}}
* '''Queen Zyanyi Arkan:''' It seems you were right Servius, the cultists wish to trigger the Gathering.
* '''Player:''' Sorry, but could someone explain what the Gathering is to me?
* '''Servius, Teokan of Ralos:''' It's the ceremony where a dead Teokan is laid to rest and their successor is chosen.
* '''Player:''' But why is it so important to the cultists?
* '''Queen Zyanyi Arkan:''' According to our recently departed iknami here, it's less about the ceremony and more about its location: The Crypt of Tonali, in the Tlati Rainforest. The cult believe the crypt houses the secret path to Mokhaiotl.
* '''Player:''' The Tlati Rainforest? Just like the nagua said...
